-- Russian c.bank shifts boundaries of rouble's trading band by 10 kopecks
-- 
-- Tue Oct 07, 2014 02:09AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Oct 7 (Reuters) - Russia's central bank has shifted its target exchange-rate corridor for the rouble by 10 kopecks, the bank said on Tuesday, following market interventions to curb the pace of the currency's decline.

